Project 1

Title: Client Management System

Description: Manage new tenders, client contacts, BD visits, sales strategy using IT platform build on Javascript, MS SQL.

Skill sets: Java development, MS SQL database

Traits expectation: ability to learn & understand the coding using e-learning tools

Expected learning: Develop complete app from UI to backend development. Discuss with teams to understand requirements and prepare business process document.

Specific courses required for project execution: Java & Database
